                    "No illegal content processing, infringement, or misuse against public order and morals.",
                    "No excessive load, abuse, or unauthorized access against the app or connected services.",
                    "No use that conflicts with applicable open-source licenses or third-party service terms."
                ]),
            new(
                "5. Disclaimers and limits of liability",
                "We do not guarantee uninterrupted operation, fitness for a specific purpose, or the quality of conversion results.",
                [
                    "Conversion can fail, lose metadata, reduce quality, or produce files with limited compatibility.",
                    "External service outages, policy changes, or shutdowns may affect some features.",
                    "Where liability cannot be excluded by law, it is limited to direct and ordinary damages."
                ]),
            new(
                "6. Provider information",
                "The provider of this app is T2 System Co., Ltd.",
                [
                    "Address: 7-20-101 Nishinosho-cho, Suita, Osaka, Japan",
                    $"Contact: {LegalDocuments.ContactUrl}"
                ])
